The Left accuses the Right of being racists. The Right accuses the Left of being socialists. We are in a political poop fest - there is a lack of intelligence in our society today on both sides. America is so fractured and I for one see little hope of a solution until those who

we voted into office to govern do just that. I have many friends who voted for Trump and still support him and I do not believe they are racist or stupid, misguided yes and frankly as shortsighted as those on the opposite side of the isle are from them. We need to be open mined

and move to the middle as a country or I fear we are heading for a titanic event in the future that will make us all sorry we didn’t compromise while it was still possible. I have made it clear how strongly I am nauseated by him and everything he stands for but my fear is if we

continue down this path our country will be torn apart with unrepairable consequences. I feel very fortunate to have been born in this country and for so many reasons -- most can understand as my family came here to get away from the oppression that they faced in Europe. I wish

somehow someway our divided government could get together and govern and I realize with the current resident in the Whitehouse that is a tall wish, but seriously we the people need someone on either side to take the gavel and be the grown up in the room.
I am tired of both sides being run by people I would not invite into my house for a cup of coffee. @realdonaldtrump @dougkass @tomkeene @jimcramer
